<HEADLINE> AP Corrects Pipeline Safety Story  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON (AP) -- The Associated Press erroneously reported in a
story about legislation to increase pipeline inspections that the
Office of Pipeline Safety is part of the National Transportation
Safety Board.
</P>
<P>
   The office is an agency of the Department of Transportation.
</P>
